Final model

reduced.env <- euro.worldclim[[c("bio10", "bio15", "bio2", "bio14", "bio5")]]
monticola.gam <- enmtools.gam(iberolacerta.clade$species$monticola,
                              reduced.env,
                              test.prop = 0.3)
interactive.plot.enmtools.model(monticola.gam)
monticola.gam
